30BarcodeFormat
31UPCEReader::expectedFormat() const
32{
33 return BarcodeFormat::UPC_E;
34}
35
36BitArray::Range
37UPCEReader::decodeMiddle(const BitArray& row, BitArray::Iterator begin, std::string& resultString) const
38{
39 BitArray::Range next = {begin, row.end()};
40 const BitArray::Range notFound = {begin, begin};
41 int lgPatternFound = 0;
42
43 for (int x = 0; x < 6; x++) {
44 int bestMatch = DecodeDigit(&next, UPCEANCommon::L_AND_G_PATTERNS, &resultString);
45 if (bestMatch == -1)
46 return notFound;
47
48 if (bestMatch >= 10) {
49 lgPatternFound |= 1 << (5 - x);
50 }
51 }
52
53 int i = IndexOf(UPCEANCommon::NUMSYS_AND_CHECK_DIGIT_PATTERNS, lgPatternFound);
54 if (i == -1)
55 return notFound;
56
57 resultString = std::to_string(i/10) + resultString + std::to_string(i % 10);
58 return {begin, next.begin};
59}
60
61bool UPCEReader::checkChecksum(const std::string& s) const
62{
63 return UPCEANReader::checkChecksum(UPCEANCommon::ConvertUPCEtoUPCA(s));
64}
65
66BitArray::Range
67UPCEReader::decodeEnd(const BitArray& row, BitArray::Iterator begin) const
68{
69 BitArray::Range next = {begin, row.end()};
70 ReadGuardPattern(&next, UPCEANCommon::UPCE_END_PATTERN);
71 return {begin, next.begin};
72}
